@startuml Login Sequence Diagram

actor User as "Pengguna"
participant Frontend as "Frontend (React)"
participant AuthController as "Auth Controller\n(Flask)"
participant Database as "Database"

User -> Frontend : Masukkan email & password
Frontend -> AuthController : **POST /login** {email, password}
AuthController -> Database : Query User by email
Database --> AuthController : Data User (jika ada)

alt Login Berhasil
    AuthController -> AuthController : Verifikasi password\n& generate JWT
    AuthController --> Frontend : 200 OK + token + data user
    Frontend -> User : Redirect ke dashboard\n(Tampilkan menu)
else Login Gagal
    AuthController --> Frontend : 401 Unauthorized\n(error message)
    Frontend -> User : Tampilkan pesan error
end

@enduml